data.title: Notes from Dean Clark (December 9, 2013)
data.text:
Notes from Dean Clark is a weekly e-newsletter produced by Dean Robert Clark and the University of Rochester Hajim School of Engineering & Applied Sciences. The newsletter is directed to the Hajim community and provides updates from the Dean about Hajim faculty, staff, and students and Hajim-related news and events. It was published from March 22, 2010-June 27, 2016.
